    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Robo Ride &amp; Glide is Not just a Kart racer</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Ride, Glide &amp; Crash through the trials of the city (and other maps!)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spend 5 minutes in a small open map, collecting upgrades, finding vehicles, and fighting your rivals -- then face off in a set of minigames to test who built the best ride!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036440/extras/d2cdd4161c816d01eb058ec67fbc8bb0.poster.avif?t=1769049656\" width=684 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036440/extras/d2cdd4161c816d01eb058ec67fbc8bb0.webm?t=1769049656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036440/extras/d2cdd4161c816d01eb058ec67fbc8bb0.mp4?t=1769049656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>One button? Many actions.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drift, trick, and spin -- don't let simplicity get confused with basic! This one button racer does the most it can with one button</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036440/extras/f74e4f1c3a79250c98ba4e10ef4d8e6e.poster.avif?t=1769049656\" width=576 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036440/extras/f74e4f1c3a79250c98ba4e10ef4d8e6e.webm?t=1769049656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036440/extras/f74e4f1c3a79250c98ba4e10ef4d8e6e.mp4?t=1769049656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiplayer!</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 4 Players try to get the best ride in a limited time! </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Some rides are better at different stats! </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face off in a random set of minigames with your upgraded rides!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Up to 8 Players when you Create custom matches with with unique rules! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036440/extras/aa02ff1f4b263b1d98c47c53a214cf47.poster.avif?t=1769049656\" width=676 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036440/extras/aa02ff1f4b263b1d98c47c53a214cf47.webm?t=1769049656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036440/extras/aa02ff1f4b263b1d98c47c53a214cf47.mp4?t=1769049656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Singleplayer Time attack scoring mode!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > try to get the high score and collect clocks to increase your time limit! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Collect power ups to Increase the stats of your ride!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Find new rides around the map!  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Get bonus points from a random mini game at the end!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036440/extras/ff99becace66ce1fd30422d747d49351.poster.avif?t=1769049656\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036440/extras/ff99becace66ce1fd30422d747d49351.webm?t=1769049656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036440/extras/ff99becace66ce1fd30422d747d49351.mp4?t=1769049656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
